fields.name: Dungeons & Dragons
fields.description: A fantasy tabletop role-playing game (RPG). D&D departs from traditional war-gaming by allowing each player to create their own character to play instead of a military formation.

fields.name: Sorry
fields.description: Bump other players' pawns and hide in your Safety Zone, where pawns of other colors can't enter.

fields.name: RuneScape
fields.description: A fantasy massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG). RuneScape takes place in the world of Gielinor, a medieval fantasy realm divided into different kingdoms, regions, and cities.
